## Conclusion

The developments currently in progress consist of refactoring the initial code,
which has a twofold objective: to stabilise the application in its construction and in
its operation and maintenance; to prepare a second version by adding additional
functionalities or those identified as missing by the community.




**Fundings / financements** : 
arabesque is developed within the framework of the project [_geographic flow visualisations (gflowiz)_](https://geoflowiz.hypotheses.org/)
an interdisciplinary collaboration initiated to design and develop a new
web application dedicated to the thematic geo-visualisation of flow and spatial network data.

